definition: name used for many fishing birds/cormorant/osprey

sentences.english: Bald eagles and ospreys roost in the old cottonwoods that line the gravel shores.
sentences.chinese: 秃鹰和鱼鹰在砾石河岸边的棉白杨林中栖息下来。

sentences.english: Osprey heat seekers work as awesome game finders.
sentences.chinese: 鱼鹰热寻求工作令人敬畏游戏观景器。

sentences.english: The exciting cormorant fishing performance is over there.
sentences.chinese: 那边有令人刺激的鱼鹰捕鱼表演。

sentences.english: A duck flies off in alarm as an osprey swoops in to catch its lunch.
sentences.chinese: 鱼鹰猛扑到池塘抓鱼作午餐的时候惊起了一只鸭子。

sentences.english: An osprey is flying over the water.
sentences.chinese: 一个鱼鹰在水面上飞翔。

sentences.english: Osprey and Blue Herons along with Bald eagles can also be seen.
sentences.chinese: 鱼鹰和蓝鹭一起白头鹰也可以看出。

sentences.english: This is the moment an osprey swooped down and snatched a trout straight out of the water.
sentences.chinese: 这是鱼鹰冲下来抓住鲑鱼出水的一霎。

sentences.english: Remember the outcryabout the Osprey's being based at Futenma?
sentences.chinese: 还记得他们强烈抗议鱼鹰驻扎在普天间基地吗？

sentences.english: These young ospreys are waiting for their parents to bring them a fish to eat.
sentences.chinese: 这些幼小的鱼鹰在等待它们的父母为他们捕回鱼来吃。

sentences.english: Blue Herons along with Bald eagles can also be seen.
sentences.chinese: 鱼鹰和蓝鹭一起白头鹰也可以看出。

definition: (bird species of China) grey heron (Ardea cinerea)
